message.body: Hey, I'm free in the morning this Friday - around 10 to 2. Are you free around then? I might also be able to do something in the evening, like around 5.
I am free from 11 to 1 on Friday. I can meet then!
Okay, let's meet around that time then. I've never been in the International House, so I'll call you when I'm in the area.
Okay! Thank you :) See you later.
